// tar 
tar cvf <file-name.tar> <files,files>  -->  to create tar files
tar xvf <file-name.tar>  --> to extract tar files

// Zip
zip <file-name.zip> <files,files>  --> to craete zip file
unzip <file-name.zip>   --> to extract the zip files

// gzip
gzip <file-name.tar>  --> to create gzip for decompress the files
gunzip <file-name.zip>  --> to remove the decompression
